Yuan Sen has already invited me.

305
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:30,520
We'll go together.

306
00:17:32,742 --> 00:17:34,782
Come on, just go!

307
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:36,160
Okay, okay.

308
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:38,480
By the way,

309
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:41,200
