332
00:18:26,782 --> 00:18:28,600
But he spends so much time worrying

333
00:18:28,811 --> 00:18:30,280
about other people.

334
00:18:31,502 --> 00:18:33,080
But he never bothers

335
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,080
