344
00:18:57,377 --> 00:18:59,291
or participates in any competitions.

345
00:19:04,114 --> 00:19:05,291
What exactly happened

346
00:19:05,948 --> 00:19:07,680
back then?

347
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,480
That day,

348
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,080
