349
00:19:14,388 --> 00:19:15,480
and the waves were rough.

350
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:17,840
But for some reason,

351
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:19,788
Sheng insisted on getting in the water.

352
00:19:21,091 --> 00:19:22,537
