353
00:19:23,365 --> 00:19:24,480
I was the one who saved him.

354
00:19:26,794 --> 00:19:28,200
Since that time,

355
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,017
he appears

356
00:19:30,045 --> 00:19:31,965
to be traumatized by water.

357
00:19:37,337 --> 00:19:39,920
You're a psychology major, right?

358
00:19:40,685 --> 00:19:42,171
Maybe you'll know what to do.

359
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,880
Besides, you're close with Sheng.

360
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:46,280
If you talk to him,

361
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:48,560
