419
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:01,131
I bought some New Year's gifts

420
00:24:01,171 --> 00:24:02,222
for everyone online.

421
00:24:02,360 --> 00:24:03,320
There's a little card

422
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,960
inside each one.

423
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:06,720
Just follow the instructions

424
00:24:06,800 --> 00:24:07,960
on your card

425
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:08,955
to complete the task.

426
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:09,755
Pass them out.

427
00:24:10,555 --> 00:24:11,311
Here you go.

428
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,040
I'll go first!

429
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:18,160
Okay, I'll read mine.

430
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:18,600
Okay.

431
00:24:23,511 --> 00:24:26,866
"Be princess-carried by someone
of the opposite sex and do five squats."

432
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:31,000
I didn't realize it would be this kind
of game when I bought them.

433
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,200
How about we forget about it?

434
00:24:32,285 --> 00:24:34,920
- No way!
- No skipping!

435
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:35,960
Come on!

436
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:37,737
No excuses!

437
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,200
Yuan Sen! Go, Yuan Sen!

438
00:24:43,645 --> 00:24:46,994
One, two, three,

439
00:24:47,188 --> 00:24:49,120
four, and five!

440
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:50,960
Unreal.

441
00:24:53,034 --> 00:24:53,880
If you ask me,

442
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,188
these aren't gifts

443
00:24:55,217 --> 00:24:56,000
