475
00:26:55,948 --> 00:26:57,657
with Han.

476
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:02,320
Why do I have to answer two questions?

477
00:27:02,688 --> 00:27:03,360
That's not fair.

478
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,520
Could it be...

479
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:11,400
